Description:
    This generator will create additional files that may be needed when creating a module.
	e.g. Controllers, Models, Serializers and Service Classes

Example:
    rails generate module_component your_module_name controller

    This will create:
        what/will/it/create
		
Example:
    rails generate module_component your_module_name serializer

    This will create:
        what/will/it/create		

Example: Creating multiple components at the same time
    rails generate module_component your_module_name controller serializer

    This will create:
        what/will/it/create		